SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c04725761
Version: 1

HPSBGN03361 rev.1 - HP UCMDB, HP UCMDB Configuration Manager, HP UCMDB
Browser, and HP Universal Discovery running TLS, Remote Disclosure of
Information

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2015-07-06
Last Updated: 2015-07-06

Potential Security Impact: Remote disclosure of information

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified with HP UCMDB, HP
UCMDB Configuration Manager, HP UCMDB Browser, and HP Universal Discovery
running TLS.

Note: This is the TLS vulnerability using US export-grade 512-bit keys in
Diffie-Hellman key exchange known as "Logjam" which could be exploited
remotely resulting in disclosure of information.

References:

CVE-2015-4000 (Remote Disclosure of Information)
SSRT102124

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.

HP UCMDB v10.01, v10.10, v10.11, v10.20
HP UCMDB Configuration Manager v10.01, v10.10, v10.11, v10.20
HP UCMDB Browser v3.21, v4.01
HP Universal Discovery v10.01,v10.10,v10.11, v10.20

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2015-4000    (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:N)       4.3
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has made the following instructions available to resolve the vulnerability
in HP UCMDB, HP UCMDB Configuration Manager, HP UCMDB Browser, and HP
Universal Discovery:

HP UCMDB: https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/
- -/facetsearch/document/KM01699134

HP UCMDB Configuration Manager: https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/software
support/search-result/-/facetsearch/document/KM01699179

HP UCMDB Browser: https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search
- -result/-/facetsearch/document/KM01699135

HP Universal Discovery: https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/
search-result/-/facetsearch/document/KM01701937

